{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Bangor Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. We run about together and that's where I stayed. And I went back home
 to my sister about - four weeks before I got married. The woman asked me to go back to get married out of our house.
