elf up that way. There's many a one that had - nothing - that's in businesses now, things like that but - there - you - you did see them going down. That was when there were no work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid605028 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13919541\charrsid12863516 If they didn't have work?
