What pay? Well - during the war we got eight shillings a day. Was a lot of money. {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Lot{\*\xmlclose} of money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid605028 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13919541\charrsid12863516 What sort of hours did you work then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5585082 SO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13919541\charrsid12863516 Well you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid142440\charrsid12863516  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13919541\charrsid12863516 m- you - maybe - stopped at five o'clock. Went 'til five. Some ti
