r finished - I went - down, and I got a house down beside my sister, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}21 Water Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. That's round the corner from Lambs House.
