as on the trawler just for a - a wee while. He was on the trawlers the time that I lost my - first wee girl. That was eleven year after it. That he went deep sea. Deep - nearly deep sea all the time. His photograph's lying by me on the top of the sideboar
d and if you seen it you would know he was a sailor.
