u had to make them make friends - because you can't allow a child to be }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12852251\charrsid12863516 prejudiced}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13919541\charrsid12863516 , don't play with her because she's so and so, oh no, I never did that.
