 with her Middes. We used to go down there and meet down there. You went in through the docks and a cross a bridge and it was just like a great - like a beach, you know. Oh we used to go to the {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Tally{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Tower{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} often.
