d to play at games and - sometimes they went out to play for a wee while. Depended on the like of day it was. Come up and they went back to Sunday school in the - Sunday afternoon. That's right. But they were always in their bed kind of early on a Sunday 
night they came in because they'd school on the Monday. It was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12852251\charrsid12863516 case of}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13919541\charrsid12863516  getting their clothes all out and everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid605028 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13919541\charrsid12863516 But you didn't mind them going out to play on a Sunday did you?
