Well I joined the Labour party because - I started to get interested in it when I used to hear the m
en speaking in the street. I've seen me standing with the children you know. And I - when I heard them speaking in the street I start - and my own life made me interested. I wondered why that people should - work hard and yet want.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid605028 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13919541\charrsid12863516 What about your husband, do you know what his views were?
