\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5585082 SO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13919541\charrsid12863516 That - oh that's correct, 
they don't bother yet. And I - I've heard them - grumbling about things and - not vote. Now I'd vote no matter who it was for. I put my vote in.
