at's no good anyone, I don't care who it is being afraid of their convictions. If you feel you want to do a thing, as long as you know that it's not - hurting anybody, or the wrong thing, that thing if you want to do a thing do it. You should never be afr
aid of your convictions. I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid605028 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13919541\charrsid12863516 When you and your husband weren't at work how did you spend your spare time?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5585082 SO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13919541\charrsid12863516 
Well - our spare time was mostly spent in the house, for one - cleaning or papering or something that's where our spare time was.
