When you got up did you get up for the whole day or did you just get up for a little while at a time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5585082 SO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13919541\charrsid12863516 
Oh - I got up - 'til I got tired. You know? I got up and - I went back to my bed at - perhaps teatime.
